{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c825478174","title":"给柳亚子的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ab7da6d497","index":0,"year":1945,"month":10,"day":4,"articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"c95885a8e7","index":1,"year":1945,"month":10,"day":7,"articleId":"c825478174"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"9820345064","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"柳亚子（一八八七——一九五八），江苏吴江人，民主主义者、诗人。当时是三民主义同志联合会负责人。"},{"id":"a45bd16ce4","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174","index":2,"part_index":3,"offset":23,"text":"柳夫人，即郑佩宜（一八八八——一九六二），江苏吴江人。当时正患盲肠炎，在重庆市立医院作手术治疗。"},{"id":"a62454983d","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174","index":3,"part_index":3,"offset":224,"text":"陆游（一一二五——一二一○），越州山阴（今浙江绍兴）人，南宋诗人。陈亮（一一四三——一一九四），婺州永康（今属浙江）人，南宋思想家、文学家。"},{"id":"2cf74c23ca","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174","index":4,"part_index":8,"offset":95,"text":"指毛泽东一九三六年二月写的《沁园春·雪》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6d8b7dcb0d","type":"title","text":"给柳亚子的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"9820345064","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"a45bd16ce4","type":"paragraph","text":"亚子先生吾兄道席：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"a62454983d","type":"paragraph","text":"诗及大示诵悉，深感勤勤恳恳诲人不倦之意。柳夫人清恙有起色否？处此严重情况，只有亲属能理解其痛苦，因而引起自己的痛苦，自非“气短”之说所可解释。时局方面，承询各项，目前均未至具体解决时期。报上云云，大都不足置信。前曾奉告二语：前途是光明的，道路是曲折的。吾辈多从曲折（即困难）二字着想，庶几反映了现实，免至失望时发生许多苦恼。而困难之克服，决不是那么容易的事情。此点深望先生引为同调。有些可谈的，容后面告，此处不复一一。先生诗慨当以慷，卑视陆游、陈亮，读之使人感发兴起。可惜我只能读，不能做。但是万千读者中多我一个读者，也不算辱没先生，我又引以自豪了。敬颂兴居安吉！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"2cf74c23ca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"134ce1b622","type":"paragraph","text":"十月四日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"555b93e78f","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"ea3b34a416","type":"paragraph","text":"亚子先生吾兄道席：","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"1df1428836","type":"paragraph","text":"迭示均悉。最后一信慨乎言之，感念最深。赤膊上阵，有时可行，作为经常办法则有缺点，先生业已了如指掌。目前发表文章、谈话，仍嫌过早。人选种种均谈不到，置之脑后为佳。初到陕北看见大雪时，填过一首词，似于先生诗格略近，录呈审正。敬颂道安！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"8b268833f6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":9,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"2e5c7a9f45","type":"paragraph","text":"十月七日","index":10,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"c8b3242428","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":11,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"},{"id":"c17c9904da","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174"}],"page":{"id":"dbcc78daa3","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"c825478174","start":43,"end":44}}}},"__N_SSG":true}